Wildrider twirls in mid air from missing his target, as he lowers to the
ground he spins in mid air facing Prowl again and continuesly moving heads
towards him again. "I knew an old Autobot named Prowl," Wildrider says
amusingly, "I hope you die half as purty (pretty) as he did, ha ha ha".
